# Curated external skills symlinked into ~/.claude/skills by setup.sh.
# Paths are relative to ~/dev/plugins (the cursor/plugins clone).
# cursor/plugins uses Cursor's .cursor-plugin manifest, so it can't be added as a
# Claude Code marketplace — we cherry-pick individual SKILL.md dirs instead.
# Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored. Edit + re-run setup.sh.
#
# Curated down from the full set (skill-audit, Barry-Zhang "don't over-engineer"):
# dropped the 10 pstack principle-* (folded into soul.md), interrogate (dup of
# adversarial-review), and speculative meta (arena, orchestrate, recall, reflect,
# show-me-your-work, figure-it-out) + the learning cluster.

